div class="t m9dc xc3 h4 y150e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">there are probably not more than 10 mil-</div><div class="t m7aa xc3 h4 y871 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">lion who are willing to devote substantial </div><div class="t ma8a xc3 h4 y915 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thought and self-discipline to maintain </div><div class="t m971 xc3 h4 y4f6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">healthy bodies. Only after they have lost </div><div class="t m98a xc3 h4 ya5c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">their health are most people willing to give </div><div class="t m3b3 xc3 h4 y146e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">any attention to the care of their bodies.&quot; </div><div class="t m42f xa3 h13 y3ab ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON OUTLINE </div><div class="t m7a0 x1c h13 y72d ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m9ec x7 h13 y82b ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Advent Movement in Prophecy </div><div class="t m19f0 x7 h13 y910 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rev. 14:12 </div><div class="t mec2 x58 h13 y2b ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t mdea x7 h13 y576 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prophecy in the Advent Movement </div><div class="t m1b11 x7 h13 yfed ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Joel 2:28, 29 </div><div class="t m2ca x58 h13 y579 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m528 xae h13 yf53 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Prophetic Guidance in Healthful </div><div class="t me4 x9f h13 y812 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Living </div><div class="t mb90 x58 h13 y155c ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m496 x7 h13 ya34 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The 1863 Health Vision </div><div class="t mb90 x1c h13 ya9f ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t mf16 xae h13 y126f ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Early Adventist Vital Statistics </div><div class="t m9b x1c h13 ya0a ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m2a5 xae h13 y198e ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Health Teaching in the Church </div><div class="t meb0 x15e h13 y1561 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">21 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.